high_descs: Turn around to walk to the black shelf on the farthest wall.
Pick up the plate from the shelf.
Turn around, then make a left after walking forwards to reach the microwave.
Heat up the plate in the microwave, removing it again.
Turn around to walk to the fridge.
Set the plate in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a plate from the shelf in the microwave to put in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the brown shelves.
Pick the plate up from the shelves.
Turn around and cross the room and turn to face the microwave.
Put the plate in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the plate out again.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Put the plate in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, proceed across room to shelf.
Pick up plate from second shelf up.
Turn around, proceed until stove on left.  Turn left, proceed to stove.
Open microwave door, place plate in microwave, shut door.  Wait three seconds, remove plate from microwave.
Open refrigerator, put plate on shelf to the right of the tomato, shut refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Move plate from shelf to microwave, heat plate, put plate in refrigerator.
